        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figures 18–25. Protohermes parcus Yang and Yang. (18) Male head and prothorax, dorsal; (19) male genitalia, dorsal view; (20) male ninth sternum, ventral view; (21) male ninth gonostylus, ventral view; (22) male tenth tergum, ventral view; (23) male tenth sternum, ventral view; (24) female abdominal apex, lateral view; (25) female eighth sternum, ventral view. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4590620/files/figure.png" .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4590614>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figures 1–5. Habitus photographs of the species in P. parcus group. (1) Protohermes congruens sp. nov., male holotype; (2) Protohermes flavinervus sp. nov., male holotype; (3) Protohermes parcus Yang and Yang, male holotype; (4) Protohermes pennyi sp. nov., male holotype; (5) Protohermes subparcus Liu and Yang, male holotype." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4590614/files/figure.png" .

